I created this pledge a few days ago, and I need you guys to help me
make it succeed.

It'll only take a moment to sign up, so please go to <?=$values['pledge_url']?>

yours,

<?=$values['creator_name']?>

This message is from Pledgebank, a service for bringing the power of your local community to your cause
